1cup brown sugar

2 large eggs

3 cups flour
2 cups (or a 12 oz bag) chocolate chips

preheat oven to 350 F

mix in sugars, eggs, butter and vanilla together.

mix dry ingredients together in a separate bowl

add dry ingredients to first bowl. then add chocolate chips.
